%% Tradeon - high-level event-driven architecture
%% Render with https://mermaid.live/ or directly in GitHub markdown
flowchart LR
    subgraph Client
        U[User / Dashboard / live_predict.py]
    end

    subgraph "Azure Container Apps"
        API[FastAPI rl-api<br/>PPO model in memory<br/>auto-scale 0 to 3]
    end

    subgraph "Event Bus"
        EG[Event Grid Topic]
        Q[Storage Queue]
        DLQ[Dead Letter Queue]
    end

    subgraph "Azure Functions"
        D[dispatcher<br/>EventGridTrigger]
        W[worker<br/>QueueTrigger]
    end

    subgraph "Persistence"
        COS[(Cosmos DB<br/>Free Tier<br/>1000 RU/s)]
    end

    subgraph "Ops"
        ACR[Container Registry<br/>tradeon-api:sha]
        AI[Application Insights]
        GH[GitHub Actions<br/>OIDC deploy.yml]
    end

    LIVE[Yahoo Finance API<br/>live OHLCV] -.->|fetch| U
    U -->|POST /predict| API
    API -->|publishes event| EG
    EG --> D
    D --> Q
    Q --> W
    W -->|calls /predict| API
    W -->|upsert decision| COS
    Q -.->|failed msgs| DLQ
    GH -->|build push image| ACR
    ACR -->|pull| API
    API -.->|telemetry| AI
    D -.->|telemetry| AI
    W -.->|telemetry| AI
